rily suspended and after about two hours, a VAR check ruled out Argentina's equalizer, declaring it to be offside.\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 768, \"end\": 771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1031928347289204e-25, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}, {\"begin\": 788, \"end\": 797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 3.829457619264026e-12, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The match\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"about two hours\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the situation was under control, the remaining three-plus minutes were played as players re-emerged in an empty stadium.\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the situation\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 859}, {\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"the remaining three-plus minutes\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"an empty stadium\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The clash finally ended in a 2-1 win for Morocco.\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999998747171, \"rank\": 1.2515219273385404e-10, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedi