 fireworks at us.\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pitch\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"fireworks\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They told us the match finished 2-2.\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1482, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"the match\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Neither we nor Morocco wanted to continue playing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1498, \"end\": 1505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999998747171, \"rank\": 1.2515219273385404e-10, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Neither we\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris Olympics football: Nothing like this ever happened - Otamendi reacts as Morocco beat Argentina Champions League: Mourinho slams UEFA after Fenerbahce's 4-3 win over Lugano AFCON: CAF dividing Africa - Senegal's Gueye speaks on returning gold medals to Morocco Moroccan club sack Senegal midfielder over AFCON 2025 title stripping remarks 'Senegal beat Morocco fair and square' - Rooney slams CAF over AFCON 2025 verdict Senegal refuses to return AFCON trophy after CAF awards title to Morocco AFCON: 'Corruption' - Senegal's Mane blasts CAF for awarding trophy to Morocco AFCON 2025: 'Daylight robbery' - Shehu Sani slams CAF for declaring Morocco winner Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 2236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1614, \"end\": 1621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999998747171, \"